reviewText: Me and my Daughter reaal enjoys all of the Case Closed DVDs. Looking for more new ones. I love how even though he's younger than the other detectives, he is very observant. We should listen to the youth maybe tell cn tell us something.

I am a real big fan of the show and like tring to figure who did it. The only problme I have with THIS DVD is that starts with ep.s 68,69,&73, what happen to the other ep.s. Ep.s 70-72 is a three part ep. my question is why did they (people who put the DVD together)skip over that case? There is about 200+ ep.s to this show and I would like to have all of them, so again why was that ep. skipped over.
